            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "It's done, but what is this...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It seems you've created something very useful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Plachta, do you know what this is?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yes. This is a tool that allows you to add catalysts to your Synthesis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Catalysts...? What's that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "To put it simply, it's like a secret ingredient for Synthesis. Catalysts can greatly increase the quality."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I didn't know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "...You made this yourself, yet you had no idea what it was?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x4a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Ehehe... I just made it because I've seen things like it a lot."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x4c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "But if it's as you said, it should make my Synthesis more effective."
        }
    ]
